<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Nyxis Levethix<br>
Wizard of the 20th circle<br>
The Rathe server. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uiudar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Iudar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/13/01 3:51:05 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Help please.....</span><hr size=1> The early 20s for me went fairly quick. <br>
<br>
<br>
The cavet is that you need to kiss your Druid faction goodbye.<br>
<br>
Treants are deffintily the way to go for fast leveling in the 20s.<br>
<br>
I decided that I had my own ports and EVACs, so why do I need it.<br>
<br>
KFC is good, as is outer paw starting around 23 (that's when I started landing more than resists).<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
To date, only once has it been a near-problem.  I stepped AFK a for minute on auto and my oh-so-not-bright group leader nearly ran me head long into one (came back about 5 steps shy of Agro).<br>
<br>
<br>
The exp is VERY fast in LOIO, if you can get a decent group.  I've been in groups there, recently as my monk, that were pulling constantly..  Others that couldn't handle more than 3 mobs without down time.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Hmmm....  I think I may try to find a couple people and camp a dr00d ring tonight.  Makes me wish Torv was PvP.... <p><TABLE ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=460 COLS=1 BORDER=1 BGCOLOR=#FF0000>
